gw.cc.policy.entity

Interface PolicySearchResultSet


  • public interface PolicySearchResultSet
    PolicySearchResultSet Result object returned by the policy admin adapter's searchPolicies() method. The result encapsulates an array of PolicySummary objects, as well as fields indicating whether or not the search results were capped, and if so, how many total results would have been returned had the results not been capped.
